text: ke ban chhlaey tha khnhom bankheunh nouv avei del puokke minban kheunh vea( chi pri l chiahseh) haey khnhom ban yk( dei) muoy kdab pi dan ( cheungseh) anakneasar( chi pri l) . kraoyomk khnhom ban baoh vea(tow leu kruengoalongkear del rleay klaycha reang kaunko) . haey khluon robsakhnhom ban phosa chea koumnit aoy khnhom thveu dauchnaoh
